## definition of type
1\. definition

+ typedef  
+ using

2\. enumeration

+ enum *TypeName* {*list of values*}
	```c++
    enum Weekday
    {SUN, MON, TUE, WED, THU, FRI, SAT}
	```
tips:
+ they cannot be evaluated to new values.
+ they can be matched with new values when defined.
	```c++
    enum Weekday
    {SUN=7, MON=1,}
  ```
+ they can be caluated.

3\. initial  

+ auto
+ decltype

